[normal]The ADASS budget survey reports that 
[normal]local authorities 
[normal]are in fact delivering more than this, achieving around 5% efficiency each year. The survey reports that 
[normal]better procurement and an increased focus on prevention are the most important ways in which councils are making savings.
[normal] Furthermore t
[normal]here are two sector-led efficiency programmes that will support 
[normal]local authorities 
[normal]over the next few years to help them to
[normal] do this.
